name: 'Best Friends'
description:
The wonders of an 
unwritten future
continuously gives us hope 
that absolutely anything
is possible - including
the impossible...
But one thing that
would always be sure, 
is no matter past, 
present or future,
we would
always be 
the best of friends...   ©   June 8 .12

name: 'Today'
description:
If there is one day

& remind you of
how grateful l am
that our souls have 
met & paths have 
crossed - well, 
it’s today… © March 07 .11

name: 'Developed Strength'
description:

Maybe it rests

trying to deal 
with both 
simultaneously... © December 5 .11
